reviewText: I loved it da wrestlers were great n hot.

This DVD is amazing value for money, featuring not one, not two, but three W.E.W. PPV's. It features all the stars of W.E.W. ODB, Lucy Furr (Daffney), Jazz, April Hunter and The Queen of Extreme herself Francine. Then if all your favourite W.E.W. stars and three PPV wasn't enough there is even a special appearance by ECW own "Studmuffin" Joel Gertner!!! If you have never watched any W.E.W. Shows, this is a great place to jump in and try the water. Highest possible rating .... Buy It.
